{"id":613165,"date":[{"year":1981,"month":5,"day":10}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"91","ytitle":"","mtitle":"赠别辛笛","ftitle":"","authors":["端木蕻良"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"端木蕻良"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛笛飞往加拿大多伦多市，参加国际诗节，赠之以诗，聊当送别。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不爱金城偏爱诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"册年未减一身痴!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飏帆吹送鸽铃远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜对西风唱楚辞。*"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*西风指英国诗人雪莱所作《西风颂》"}]}